Hannah Ware https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hannah_Ware 0 Hannah Rose Ware (born 8 December 1982) is an English actress, best known for her roles as Emma Kane in the Starz political drama series Boss (2011–2012) and as Sara Hanley in the ABC primetime soap opera Betrayal (2013–2014).
